    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device at MRL 2. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed; all assessed factors met or exceeded required levels. The remaining six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for the relative hemolysis index across the COU operating envelope.",
